OL,3,CVictims of infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'battling for truth'
OL,6,FThose whose lives have been impacted
OL,7,Fby the have gathered in Westminster,
OL,8,Fcalling on the Government for justice
OL,9,Fand compensation.
OL,11,FIt's thought up to as many as thirty
OL,12,Fthousand men, women and children were
OL,13,Finfected with and Hepatitis C during
OL,14,Fthe 1970s and 80s due to contaminated
OL,15,Fblood products.
OL,17,FThousands of people have since died
OL,18,Fand campaigners stood outside
OL,19,Fparliament to protest against the lack
OL,20,Fof progress on compensation, while
OL,21,Fpeople affected continue to die.
