OL,6,FAndy Evans, the founder of the Tainted
OL,7,FBlood campaign group, told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral his life has been a
OL,9,F"rollercoaster of illness" and a
OL,10,F"battle for justice".
OL,12,FAndy, who is a haemophiliac, was
OL,13,Finfected with HIV and Hepatitis C when
OL,14,Fhe was just 5 years old.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
