OL,3,CVictims of infected blood scandal
OL,4,C'battling for truth'
OL,6,F"I was told by my parents when I was
OL,7,Fthirteen because I started to become
OL,8,Fill with HIV symptoms, I was diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith full-blown AIDS when I was
OL,10,Fsixteen", he explains. "I spent most
OL,11,Fof the next four years in and out of
OL,12,Fhospital until I was thankfully saved
OL,13,Fby new combination therapies that came
OL,14,Fout."
OL,16,FAndy later had to face Hepatitis C and
OL,17,Fthe treatments that came with that
OL,18,Fdiagnosis.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
