OL,4,C'battling for truth'
OL,6,F"I'm here to make one final push
OL,7,Ftowards the proper justice and
OL,8,Fcompensation for people who have been
OL,9,Ffighting now for forty years to get
OL,10,Fsome sort of redress for this
OL,11,Fscandal", says Andy.
OL,13,F"I've headed up a campaign group since
OL,14,F2006 on this - the aims of which were
OL,15,Fto achieve compensation, a public
OL,16,Finquiry which we now have and
OL,17,Fhopefully at some point a full apology
OL,18,Ffrom the people who were involved in
OL,19,Fthe 70s and 80s."
