OL,6,FAndy maintains that warnings in the
OL,7,Fearly stages of the scandal were
OL,8,Fignored and many people could have
OL,9,Fbeen saved if more had been done.
OL,11,F"We're battling to get the truth known
OL,12,Fand justice to be served", he adds.
OL,14,FRos Cooper, from Bewdley in , had a
OL,15,Frare blood disorder similar to
OL,16,Fhaemophilia, which required treatment
OL,17,Fwith blood products.
