OL,6,FShe was diagnosed with Hepatitis C
OL,7,Fwhen she was nineteen and says it's
OL,8,Fnot just her physical health that has
OL,9,Fbeen impacted.
OL,11,FShe says for her it's about much more
OL,12,Fthan money or compensation.
OL,14,F"People like myself who have been
OL,15,Firreversibly damaged by this, not just
OL,16,Fphysically but mentally. My entire
OL,17,Flife has been derailed from the age of
OL,18,Fnineteen when I found out. You can't
OL,19,Fput a figure on that", she says.
