OL,6,FRosemary says she was informed about
OL,7,Fher son's condition in a letter when
OL,8,Fhe was 11 years old and they were
OL,9,F"left to get on with it".
OL,11,FNicky died when he was 25, leaving
OL,12,Fbehind a young widow and a 1 year old
OL,13,Fbaby.
OL,15,FRosemary says there was a huge stigma
OL,16,Fwhich meant her family had to mostly
OL,17,Fstruggle in silence. She now runs a
OL,18,Fsupport group for other mothers who
OL,19,Fhave been impacted by the scandal.
