OL,6,F"I've been without Nicky almost as
OL,7,Flong I was with him", she says. "How
OL,8,Fmany more are going to die without
OL,9,Fseeing justice?"
OL,11,FWhat is the Infected Blood Inquiry?
OL,13,FIt has been referred to as the the
OL,14,Fbiggest treatment disaster in NHS
OL,15,Fhistory - and a public inquiry has
OL,16,Fbeen taking evidence since 2019 from
OL,17,Fvictims infected and affected by the
OL,18,Fscandal.
