OL,6,FAn interim report was published in
OL,7,FSpring 2023, recommending for a
OL,8,Fcompensation scheme to immediately be
OL,9,Fset up.
OL,11,FSir Brian Longstaff, who is chairing
OL,12,Fthe inquiry, also recommended that
OL,13,Fparents and children of people who
OL,14,Freceived infected blood should receive
OL,15,Fcompensation.
OL,17,FThe final report is due in May.
