OL,6,FThe Government's is waiting for the
OL,7,Ffinal report from the public inquiry -
OL,8,Fdue in May - before setting out their
OL,9,Fapproach to full compensation.
OL,11,FSpeaking during Prime Minister's
OL,12,FQuestions today, Rishi Sunak said:
OL,13,F"We've consistently acknowledged that
OL,14,Fjustice should be delivered. I gave
OL,15,Fevidence to the public inquiry last
OL,16,Fyear.
