OL,6,F"The government has accepted the moral
OL,7,Fcase for compensation, which is why -
OL,8,Fon Monday, in the other place (The
OL,9,FHouse of Lords) - we committed to
OL,10,Fbringing forward amendments at report
OL,11,Fstage of the Victim and Prisoners
OL,12,FBill, with the intention of speeding
OL,13,Fup the implementation of our response
OL,14,Fto the Infected Blood Inquiry."
